    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mint sauce </strong>and a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> and give everything a good mix – this is your <strong>minty yoghurt dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
